Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This year's Christmas present is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.43,0:00:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For... Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'll definitely go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.61,0:00:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.49,0:00:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a week early, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.70,0:00:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.97,0:00:44.85,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Usotsuki na anata nakimushi no atashi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.85,0:00:50.82,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doushite umaku ikanai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:56.95,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Oshare shita kami mo rain suton no tsume mo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.95,0:01:02.91,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata wa kidzuki mo shinai ne
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.91,0:01:10.29,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love kanashii namida nanka ja nai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.29,0:01:15.01,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Me ga kawaite hirihiri suru dake
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:20.93,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kono unmei bakari I love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.85,0:01:29.81,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi dake wo atashi dake wo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.81,0:01:34.74,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Atsui omoi wo uketomete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.95,0:01:41.87,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doko made mo tsunagattetai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:48.62,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawaikunai nakigao mo se mo aishiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.97,0:00:44.85,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't things go well between
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.85,0:00:50.82,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,the liar, you, and the crybaby, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:56.95,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't notice my styled hair
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.95,0:01:02.91,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,or my nice set of press-on nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.91,0:01:10.29,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love isn't about the unhappy tears that go along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.29,0:01:15.01,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Those tears only leave my eyes dry and hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:20.93,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I love this destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.85,0:01:29.81,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,between only you and only me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.81,0:01:34.74,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to accept your hot feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.95,0:01:41.87,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,and be taken by you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:48.62,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite your uncute, tearful face and your shortness, I still love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with my mom to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:02:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can imagine, going to Tokyo Disneyland would be a bit much, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for Christmas, we can play around at the Asahigawa Zoo and then go to a hot spring afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.06,0:02:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hot spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.69,0:02:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we can spend the entire day together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The entire day together?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.32,0:02:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be spending the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay if we just fall asleep holding hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.79,0:02:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what you want, I promise not to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.91,0:02:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's it sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's it sound? Impossible. You don't have that kind of cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're worried about money, I'll take care of it somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I already did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.47,0:02:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, I'd like to get my allowance early.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to spend it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to spend Christmas with my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not an amount a high schooler could spend in a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:02:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really want to spoil her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm making you a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...go with you to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that your... atonement?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.97,0:03:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, then I don't want you to take it that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we honest today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.01,0:03:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi, I want to make this a Christmas you'll love.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who really wants to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.23,0:03:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want this to be a Christmas you'll remember, so even when we're apart for a year, you'll feel like you can stick with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you said you didn't believe in memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I'm not very honest with my feelings, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, umm... if you leave the hot spring out...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I don't understand what you're getting at...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your feelings really hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared of this "something special."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know we only have a little time left...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.91,0:04:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but that's exactly why I want to spend our time together like we always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like any other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to believe that it's not something special, and that it's not an ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so cute...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...! I knew I should've forced you to go to that hot spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, you don't know when to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You promised we'd spend today like we would any other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say that to yourself! You're different from normal! You're no fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you look really cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please look at the sky to your left.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In December, the winter constellations illuminate the eastern sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It does exist. I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it feels so warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your heart does?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna take a picture. Come on, smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy should be able to win the toy at times like these, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like in the last episode of those TV soap operas...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the girlfriend smiles when you win it, and it's a happy ending, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... but this isn't some soap opera or anime, so don't be so sulky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm gonna press the button!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? I've got such a weird face!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? It's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sticker machine loves you, Yano. It plays favorites and leaves me in the dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so sulky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.48,0:07:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my girlfriend was a cheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, when I confessed the scars of my past...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we go get our picture taken at a photo booth together?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you an idiot or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.33,0:07:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I thought I was, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You big moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so much of a moron... that I fell in love with a person I hated so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it might be a good thing that you were a moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty cute in that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... in this one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first... picture sticker we took together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so awkward back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and we were both... so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano... did you bring that with you today on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's it look on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you're in Tokyo, send me tons of pictures, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like how you look in your uniform... and lots more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we're apart, we're really just a second away, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.12,0:10:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be able to hear your voice, I'll be able to see your face, and we can e-mail each other, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...may not be able to call you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My family's finances are a little tight right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll call at least once a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:10:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna look for a part-time job there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A part-time job?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be okay with the entrance exams?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let my mother worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is there something on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That we'll definitely meet in Tokyo a year from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until then, I won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.19,0:12:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...fall for anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:13:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...before we knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we become older than Nana-san was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very happy that you feel that way about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you'll just end up wasting your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.58,0:13:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.58,0:13:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you I didn't need your answer yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you say you won't fall for anyone but him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a year from now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.89,0:13:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even five years from now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think you know the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because... I promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:14:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...broke my promise once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.19,0:14:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I pushed Yano away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I betrayed Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you wanted to protect me, Takeuchi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I want to protect Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom... I'm going to go to college in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? You said you were going to a public school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.31,0:14:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to stay here in the countryside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to leave me alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you'll go whether you have my permission or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because there's something I want in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:15:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something I want... more than anything else in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.26,0:15:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that face?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana, you look awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cried so much last night, and I looked like this when I woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face looks really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get a cooling pad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Lalami?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.23,0:15:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, I'm leaving her with my grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna scout things out first, and if I can bring her to the apartment in Tokyo, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, here's my address.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawasaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My college is in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only thirty minutes from Shibuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mizuguchi. Where's Takahashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:47.21,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,300)\an8\c&HA26F58&\b1\fs36\pos(320,2)}Sign: Cooling Pads
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-She's in the bathroom right now! Hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she taking a crap?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Seems like a really long one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.47,0:15:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makes you wonder what she ate, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really won't come back at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have that kind of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even over summer and spring break?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.39,0:16:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sucks... on a day like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the swelling will go down...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't Yano looking for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I made an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.57,0:16:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Mizu-chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I really won't see you until you get accepted into college, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on. You're fine now, so go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are resolute with your decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I thought, I'm gonna cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much will I regret this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I just going to repeat the same things over and over again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ask me if I want to go, my answer is of course no.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ask me if I'll be fine once I get there, of course I won't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always asked my girlfriends to stay by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:17:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I thought I'd promised myself not to let them out of my sight ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I won't do anything to her while you're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.01,0:17:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I so nice?! Am I a total idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, playing unfairly just doesn't feel right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a reason to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you let your guard down, or really take your eyes off of her...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll steal her from you in a heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real battle starts after you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait and see what happens a year from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the sigh of relief?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.72,0:18:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just couldn't stand it when you two studied together or went to the library together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.06,0:18:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I'll still do that. That's fair, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what about going to the summer festival with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... it seems like you'd probably do something to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.61,0:18:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong. I'd go as a friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.23,0:18:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give them some time alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever you go...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However lonely you get...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.26,0:18:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll be here, thinking of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.35,0:18:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're definitely not alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.86,0:18:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"It all equals out," was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, you may not have someone left who you really, really love...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and that might be a really sad thing for you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because there are people out there who really, really love you, shouldn't it all equal out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... please don't think you're all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.27,0:19:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't all equal out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It ended up more equal... on the positive side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:20:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I met you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I feel like...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I've lived to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were all indeed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.99,0:22:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We lived here...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.24,0:22:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to love him...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.29,0:22:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I loved her...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.92,0:22:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Receiving so many beginnings...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.26,0:22:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and a countless number of feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.97,0:22:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Learning each other's strengths and weaknesses...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.91,0:23:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.08,0:23:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.29,0:23:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.06,0:25:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:22:02.21,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Ima kimi ga iikaketa kotoba ga
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.21,0:22:08.64,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Yubisaki ni sotto oritekita
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.64,0:22:15.06,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanimo iwanakute ii yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.06,0:22:21.07,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumaida yubi wo gyutto atatamete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.07,0:22:37.75,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotoba wa kotoba dakara kokoro hanbun mo tsutaenai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.75,0:22:50.47,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Setsunakute modokashikute yuuyake futari wo tsutsundeiru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.47,0:23:04.19,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Komiageru mune no omoi kokoro ga itai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.03,0:23:14.37,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Moshi kimi ga tabibito ni nattara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.37,0:23:20.83,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Dore gurai kimi wo matteru darou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.83,0:23:27.63,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kisetsu wa kawaru sono tabi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.63,0:23:33.55,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kioku ga usuragu koto ga attemo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.55,0:23:49.36,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Dareka wo konna fuu ni kokoro ippai de aisenai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.36,0:23:57.12,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamaritai taisetsu na kimi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.12,0:24:03.04,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Itsu datte futari wa hitori ja nai
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.04,0:24:10.72,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kono mune ga kawaresou de
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.72,0:24:16.51,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Furete hoshii yo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.97,0:24:33.03,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Setsunakute modokashikute kaerenai kono mama aruiteitai
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.03,0:24:48.13,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Yabaisaki ni kanjiteiru kokoro no kotoba wo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:22:02.21,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,The words you were just about to say
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.21,0:22:08.64,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,fell softly onto my fingertips.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.64,0:22:15.06,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.06,0:22:21.07,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll clasp your hand tightly and warm it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.07,0:22:37.75,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Because words are words, I can't express half of the feelings in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.75,0:22:50.47,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so wrenching and irritating as the sunset engulfs the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.47,0:23:04.19,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart aches from all the feelings welling up inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.03,0:23:14.37,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were to become a traveler,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.37,0:23:20.83,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,would I be able to wait for you as I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.83,0:23:27.63,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,As the seasons change,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.63,0:23:33.55,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,even if our memories are to fade.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.55,0:23:49.36,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be able to love someone with all of my heart like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.36,0:23:57.12,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to protect the precious you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.12,0:24:03.04,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us are never alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.04,0:24:10.72,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Me heart feels so fragile
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.72,0:24:16.51,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,and I want you to touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.97,0:24:33.03,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so wrenching and irritating that I can't go home. I want to keep walking like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.03,0:24:48.13,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel the words from your heart on my fingertips.
